[142.54227, "o", "\r\nрџ“Љ Sweep Summary:\r\n   Dust inputs:  3\r\n   Total dust:   1600 sats\r\n\r\nрџ§№ Sweep PSBT (base64):\r\\r\n\r\nрџ’Ў Next steps:\r\n   Inspect: bitcoin-cli -rpcport=18443 -rpcuser=user -rpcpassword=pass decodepsbt <psbt>\r\n   Sign:    bitcoin-cli -rpcport=18443 -rpcuser=user -rpcpassword=pass walletprocesspsbt <psbt>\r\n   Send:    bitcoin-cli -rpcport=18443 -rpcuser=user -rpcpassword=pass sendrawtransaction <hex>\r\n"]
